			<P><STRONG>"Has your strategy been effective against Pandemonium on Tallon Zek?"</STRONG></P>
<P><STRONG></STRONG>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Much like other pvp servers (I am assuming, only play on TZ myself), the top guild has solidified their position due to the flag system. Through whatever tactics neccesary, they prevent guilds below them from progressing. No amount of strategy can overcome the flag system.</P>
<P>If you were talking about individual or small group fighting, PDM is in time/GoD gear while everyone else is in partial elemental at best. The incredible hp/ac/resist gap nullifies the use of much strategy. A monkey banging on the keyboard in time/god gear could beat me any day of the week.</P>
<P>Can only imagine what its like on Sullon where the lights are only in vex thal gear.</P>
